msgid ""
"Invariant can be specified in the state label (not the node name!) separated "
"by ``\\n``::"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../trace/rv/hybrid_automata.rst:305
msgid ""
"Constraints can be specified as valid C comparisons and allow spaces, the "
"first element of the comparison must be the clock while the second is a "
"numerical or parametrised value. Guards allow comparisons to be combined "
"with boolean operations (``&&`` and ``||``), resets must be separated from "
"other constraints."
msgstr ""

